Package org.jqassistant.plugin.c4.antlr

Class C4BaseListener

java.lang.Object
org.jqassistant.plugin.c4.antlr.C4BaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, C4Listener
Direct Known Subclasses:
C4ParseListener
public class C4BaseListener extends Object implements C4Listener
This class provides an empty implementation of C4Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
